<paragraph blockId="5.[816,1429,489,683]" box="[816,1019,489,515]" pageId="5" pageNumber="75">
<emphasis box="[816,1019,489,515]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="75">Ecological Notes</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[816,1429,489,683]" pageId="5" pageNumber="75">All roosts were found in caves except for one tree roost where a single individual was located. Numbers were typically in single figures, although up to 21 bats were recorded at one site. Although widespread, this species was not abundant.</paragraph>
